    {
      "id": "task-semantics",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Semantic Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 2313.833333333333,
        "y": -2137.2463113334816
      },
      "width": 540,
      "height": 300,
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "any",
          "position": {
            "side": "left",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "any",
          "position": {
            "side": "right",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Required Target Contract\n\nReference-capable nodes normalize to:\n\n- `data.target.kind`: `graph` | `fragment` | `document`\n- `data.target.ref`: canonical ref (`github://`, `tlz://`, local path)\n- `data.target.entryPort`: default `root`\n- `data.target.mode`: `navigate` | `expand` | `bridge`\n\nCurrent rules:\n\n- `mode=navigate` replaces the host graph/session.\n- `mode=expand` projects the target into the current host session.\n- `mode=expand` is valid for fragments and full graph documents.\n- `mode=bridge` is explicit capability import inside the current session.\n- authority does not transfer just because content became visible.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
