    {
      "id": "task-safe-merge-idempotency",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Safe Merge + Idempotency Policy",
      "position": {
        "x": 5960,
        "y": 500
      },
      "width": 700,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "any",
          "position": {
            "side": "left",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "any",
          "position": {
            "side": "right",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Safe Merge + Idempotency (No Canonical ID Rewrite)\n\nGoal: prevent collisions without breaking source identity.\n\n## Rules\n\n1. Preserve source canonical IDs\n- Keep fragment `node.id` as canonical identity metadata.\n\n2. Materialize with runtime instance keys\n- Host materialized key: `instanceId:canonicalId` (runtime/internal).\n- Store provenance:\n  - `data._origin.canonicalId`\n  - `data._origin.ref`\n  - `data._origin.instanceId`\n\n3. Idempotency key\n- `expandKey = sourceNodeId + ref + entryPort + mode`\n- If `expandKey` exists: reuse/focus existing expansion, do not duplicate.\n\n4. Collision handling\n- Same `canonicalId` in same `instanceId`: reuse (idempotent).\n- Same `canonicalId` in different instances: allowed via distinct runtime keys.\n- Legacy flat-ID collision with no provenance: safe-fail with explicit error.\n\n5. Collapse semantics\n- Collapse by `instanceId`/provenance, never by raw canonical IDs.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
