    {
      "id": "task-rollback-semantics-v1",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Rollback Semantics (V1 Decision)",
      "position": {
        "x": 8240,
        "y": 500
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 460,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "any",
          "position": {
            "side": "left",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "any",
          "position": {
            "side": "right",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Rollback Semantics (V1 Decision)\n\nAccepted decisions:\n\n1. Expansion is all-or-nothing transaction.\n2. Every injected node/edge carries `expansionId` provenance.\n3. On expansion failure, rollback all entities from current `expansionId`.\n4. Collapse removes only entities tied to target `expansionId`.\n5. If user edits injected node, it must be explicitly promoted before excluding from collapse.\n6. Failures return specific error code + message (no silent partial state).\n\nOperational distinction:\n\n- **Transactional rollback**: automatic on failed expand.\n- **Collapse detach**: user-initiated removal by provenance.\n\nAcceptance:\n\n- No partial branch artifacts remain after failed expansion.\n- Host-authored content is never removed by collapse.\n- Promoted nodes survive collapse by design.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
